%div.page-header
  %h1 About #{PRODUCT_DISPLAY_NAME}
%p
  %i.icon-ok
  #{PRODUCT_DISPLAY_NAME} 
  is a place where you can easily create timelines and then share them with your friends. Do you want to create a timeline for your history project? Or do you want to display your company's progress through the years? This is the place for it!
%p
  %i.icon-ok
  It already has hundreds of thousands of events - seeded from Wikipedia. You can use these to create a timeline of your choice. You can, of course, add new events as well, while creating your timeline.
%p
  %i.icon-ok
  Visit the
  %a{:href => showcase_path }showcase
  to see a few selected timelines.
%p
  %i.icon-ok
  Excited? Login and get your hands
  %a{:href => new_timeline_path}dirty.

